item.title: 22 May 2019 16:27
item.description: Flew into Joberg after a 4 hour layover in Addis Ababa for a day to take the IMST. Today I guess, is one lucky day! Realised only after reaching the Pearson Vue test center that I flew in a week early. Got the dates wrong! Thankfully, the proctor managed to re-schedule the test…and I passed! On to the next stage…
